  "game_log": [
    "Welcome to Plainstown!",
    "Thelma: Hail new arrivals! I hear you are in need of coin and more to aid in your adventures. I have a problem that I think you can solve. Maybe we can make a deal? I am the shop owner and I've found myself with a Graint Rat problem and I suspect it may be even worse. They are in my shop and in my basement. If you would deal with that problem I can make it worth your while! I have some extra Camping Supplies that I think may be real worthwhile. Deal?",
    "Thelma: Wonderful! I'm counting on you. Good luck out there!",
